        "en": "Chapter 1. Demand &amp; Supply<br>Chapter 2. Elasticities of Supply and Demand and Equilibrium<br>Chapter 3. Consumer Behavior<br>Chapter 4. Producer Behavior<br>Chapter 5. National Income<br>Chapter 6. Economic Indicators<br>Chapter 7. Economic Growth<br>"
    },
    "weeklySchedule": "Week 1    課程概述 <br>Week 2    經濟問題與經濟學<br>Week 3    分工與市場：生活水準提升的泉源<br>Week 4    個人如何做選擇<br>Week 5    行為經濟學<br>Week 6    行為經濟學<br>Week 7    商業組織與金融資本、企業的運作<br>Week 8    完全競爭市場<br>Week 9    期中考試<br>Week 10   自由競爭與獨占<br>Week 11   生產要素的角色和收入本質<br>Week 12   政府與經濟活動<br>Week 13   衡量整體經濟活動：國民所得的概念<br>Week 14   失業與通貨膨脹<br>Week 15   貨幣與金融體系<br>Week 16   總體經濟政策<br>Week 17   Holiday<br>Week 18   期末考試",
